siteMetadata.title: Victory in Jesus
siteMetadata.subtitle: We can have victory because Our Lord and Savior conquered Sin and Death!

frontmatter.title: Easter Hope
frontmatter.description: He has risen! He has risen indeed! Those words bring so much joy to a christians heart. When jesus ressurected from the dead He brought so much hope to the world.

frontmatter.title: We can have Victory with Jesus Christ
frontmatter.description: The passage of Matthew 4 is one of the greatest inspirational messages. It's a clear example of how we can overcome any trial in life.
